I know the title of this review is corny but these are two of my favorite westerns.  Both are dated since they were two of Eastwoods first but great non-the-less.  I am a big Eastwood fan.  I got this for $5.00 through Amazon froma vendor advertised as "used" .  They were in perfect shape. So the question is "Do you feel lucky?".  I'll buy used again.  BTW his best movie of all time is Grand Torino.
